Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.41,0:26:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.18,0:26:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的學妹不可能那麽腐
